text: Amblymora samarensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1947. It is known from the Philippines.BioLib.cz - Amblymora samarensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Amblymora Category:Beetles described in 1947
